List Available SI-PNI Years

Source: R/sipni.R
sipni_years.Rd

Returns an integer vector with years for which vaccination data are available from DATASUS FTP.

Usage

sipni_years()

Value

An integer vector of available years (1994–2019).

Details

SI-PNI data on the DATASUS FTP is available from 1994 to 2019. All data is definitive (no preliminary/final distinction). Post-2019 data requires the SI-PNI web API (not yet supported).

See also

Other sipni: sipni_cache_status(), sipni_clear_cache(), sipni_data(), sipni_dictionary(), sipni_info(), sipni_variables()

Examples

sipni_years()
#>  [1] 1994 1995 1996 1997 1998 1999 2000 2001 2002 2003 2004 2005 2006 2007 2008
#> [16] 2009 2010 2011 2012 2013 2014 2015 2016 2017 2018 2019
